verbose_text: Furthermore, Ad5.pIX-gp70 vaccination induced a significantly higher frequency of GzmB + cells in splenic host effector CD44 + IFN-gamma + CD8 + T cells than FV infection did (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), arguing that the difference between the two immunogens was not restricted to CD4 + T cells or to TCR (T cell-receptor)-transgenic T cells.
